description: David Sanborn graces the Backstage Pass stage to share a few funny stories and to reflect on his insecurities, sobriety and how music saved his life. Join The Smooth Jazz Cruise email list for cruise updates and more news about your favorite artists: http://www.thesmoothjazzcruise.com/join-our-email-list
title: David Sanborn - Backstage Pass
